\v 7 Ali, o homem <a name="01802300700004" ll="SDBH:יָשָׁר:000004">reto</a> <a name="01802300700006" ll="SDBH:יכח:000001">pleitearia</a> com ele,e <a name="01802300700012" ll="SDBH:פלט:000001">eu</a> <a name="01802300700012" ll="SDBH:פלט:000001">me</a> <a name="01802300700012" ll="SDBH:פלט:000001">livraria</a> para <a name="01802300700016" ll="SDBH:נֵצַח:000000">sempre</a> do <a name="01802300700020" ll="SDBH:שׁפט:000006" il="Tel-dan-israelite-gate-im-tor" tl="HOTTP1920">meu</a> <a name="01802300700020" ll="SDBH:שׁפט:000006" il="Tel-dan-israelite-gate-im-tor" tl="HOTTP1920">juiz</a>.
    
\v 8 Eis que, <a name="01802300800004;01802300800006" ll="SDBH:הלך:000001;SDBH:קֶדֶם:000001">se</a> <a name="01802300800004;01802300800006" ll="SDBH:הלך:000001;SDBH:קֶדֶם:000001">me</a> <a name="01802300800004;01802300800006" ll="SDBH:הלך:000001;SDBH:קֶדֶם:000001">adianto</a>, ali não está;se torno <a name="01802300800014" ll="SDBH:אָחֹור:000001">para</a> <a name="01802300800014" ll="SDBH:אָחֹור:000001">trás</a>, não o <a name="01802300800020" ll="SDBH:בין:000001">percebo</a>.
    
