\v 2 Como <a name="01802600200004" ll="SDBH:עזר:000001">sabes</a> <a name="01802600200004" ll="SDBH:עזר:000001">ajudar</a> ao que <a name="01802600200008" ll="SDBH:לֹא:000000">não</a> <a name="01802600200010" ll="SDBH:כֹּחַ:000000">tem</a> <a name="01802600200010" ll="SDBH:כֹּחַ:000000">força</a>e <a name="01802600200012" ll="SDBH:ישׁע:000001">prestar</a> <a name="01802600200012" ll="SDBH:ישׁע:000001">socorro</a> ao <a name="01802600200014" ll="SDBH:זְרֹועַ:000000">braço</a> que não tem <a name="01802600200018" ll="SDBH:עֹז:000002">vigor</a>!
    
