\v 13 Pelo <a name="01802601300004" ll="SDBH:רוּחַ:000004" il="Gale_Force_Winds">seu</a> <a name="01802601300004" ll="SDBH:רוּחַ:000004" il="Gale_Force_Winds">sopro</a> <a name="01802601300008" ll="SDBH:שִׁפְרָה:000000">aclara</a> os <a name="01802601300006" ll="SDBH:שָׁמַיִם:000000">céus</a>,a <a name="01802601300012">sua</a> <a name="01802601300012">mão</a> fere o <a name="01802601300014" ll="SDBH:נָחָשׁ:000000" il="ArbeLevy-Vipera_palaestinae_4;Fauna:4.9a;Fauna:4.9b">dragão</a> <a name="01802601300016" ll="SDBH:בָּרִחַ:000000">veloz</a>.
    
\v 14 Eis que isto são apenas as <a name="01802601400006" ll="SDBH:קָצָה:000001">orlas</a> <a name="01802601400010" ll="SDBH:דֶּרֶךְ:000007">dos</a> <a name="01802601400010" ll="SDBH:דֶּרֶךְ:000007">seus</a> <a name="01802601400010" ll="SDBH:דֶּרֶךְ:000007">caminhos</a>!Que <a name="01802601400016;01802601400018" ll="SDBH:דָּבָר:000000;SDBH:שֵׁמֶץ:000000">leve</a> <a name="01802601400016;01802601400018" ll="SDBH:דָּבָר:000000;SDBH:שֵׁמֶץ:000000">sussurro</a> <a name="01802601400020">temos</a> <a name="01802601400020">ouvido</a> dele!Mas o <a name="01802601400026" ll="SDBH:רַעַם:000000">trovão</a> <a name="01802601400030" ll="SDBH:גְּבוּרָה:000002">do</a> <a name="01802601400030" ll="SDBH:גְּבוּרָה:000002">seu</a> <a name="01802601400030" ll="SDBH:גְּבוּרָה:000002">poder</a>, quem o <a name="01802601400034" ll="SDBH:בין:000002">entenderá</a>?
