\v 1 <a name="01802700100004;01802700100008" ll="SDBH:נשׂא:000048">Prosseguindo</a> <a name="01802700100006" ll="SDBH:אִיֹּוב:000000">Jó</a> em <a name="01802700100010" ll="SDBH:מָשָׁל:000000">seu</a> <a name="01802700100010" ll="SDBH:מָשָׁל:000000">discurso</a>, <a name="01802700100014" ll="SDBH:אמר:000000">disse</a>:
    
