\v 3 <a name="01802700300006">enquanto</a> em mim estiver a <a name="01802700300008" ll="SDBH:נְשָׁמָה:000000">minha</a> <a name="01802700300008" ll="SDBH:נְשָׁמָה:000000">vida</a>,e o <a name="01802700300014" ll="SDBH:רוּחַ:000003">sopro</a> de <a name="01802700300016" ll="SDBH:אֱלֹוהַּ:000001">Deus</a> nos <a name="01802700300020" ll="SDBH:אַף:000001">meus</a> <a name="01802700300020" ll="SDBH:אַף:000001">narizes</a>,
    
