\v 5 <a name="01802700500002" ll="SDBH:חֲלִילָה:000000">Longe</a> de mim que <a name="01802700500008" ll="SDBH:צדק:000003">eu</a> vos <a name="01802700500008" ll="SDBH:צדק:000003">dê</a> <a name="01802700500008" ll="SDBH:צדק:000003">razão</a>!Até <a name="01802700500014" ll="SDBH:גוע:000000">que</a> <a name="01802700500014" ll="SDBH:גוע:000000">eu</a> <a name="01802700500014" ll="SDBH:גוע:000000">expire</a>, nunca <a name="01802700500018" ll="SDBH:סור:000008">afastarei</a> de mim a <a name="01802700500020" ll="SDBH:תֻּמָּה:000000">minha</a> <a name="01802700500020" ll="SDBH:תֻּמָּה:000000">integridade</a>.
    
