\v 22 Deus <a name="01802702200004" ll="SDBH:שׁלך:000000">lança</a> isto sobre ele e não <a name="01802702200012" ll="SDBH:חמל:000002">o</a> <a name="01802702200012" ll="SDBH:חמל:000002">poupa</a>,a <a name="01802702200018;01802702200020" ll="SDBH:ברח:000000">ele</a> que <a name="01802702200018;01802702200020" ll="SDBH:ברח:000000">procura</a> <a name="01802702200018;01802702200020" ll="SDBH:ברח:000000">fugir</a> <a name="01802702200018;01802702200020" ll="SDBH:ברח:000000">precipitadamente</a> da <a name="01802702200016">sua</a> <a name="01802702200016">mão</a>;
    
