\v 11 <a name="01802801100008" ll="SDBH:חבשׁ:000001" tl="HOTTP1954">Tapa</a> os <a name="01802801100006" ll="SDBH:נָהָר:000000" tl="HOTTP1953">veios</a> de <a name="01802801100004" ll="SDBH:בְּכִי:000000;SDBH:מַבָּךְ:000000" tl="HOTTP1953">água</a>, e nem uma gota sai deles,e <a name="01802801100014" ll="SDBH:יצא:000001">traz</a> à <a name="01802801100016" ll="SDBH:אֹור:000000">luz</a> <a name="01802801100012" ll="SDBH:תַּעֲלֻמָה:000000">o</a> <a name="01802801100012" ll="SDBH:תַּעֲלֻמָה:000000">que</a> <a name="01802801100012" ll="SDBH:תַּעֲלֻמָה:000000">estava</a> <a name="01802801100012" ll="SDBH:תַּעֲלֻמָה:000000">escondido</a>.
    
