\v 24 <a name="01803602400002" ll="SDBH:זכר:000000">Lembra</a>-te de <a name="01803602400008" ll="SDBH:פֹּעַל:000000">lhe</a> <a name="01803602400006" ll="SDBH:שׂגא:000001">magnificares</a> <a name="01803602400008" ll="SDBH:פֹּעַל:000000">as</a> <a name="01803602400008" ll="SDBH:פֹּעַל:000000">obras</a>que os homens <a name="01803602400012" ll="SDBH:שׁיר:000000" il="HK00188">celebram</a>.
    
