\v 32 <a name="01803603200006" ll="SDBH:כסה:000000;SDBH:כסה:000001">Enche</a> as <a name="01803603200004" ll="SDBH:כַּף:000000">mãos</a> <a name="01803603200008" ll="SDBH:אֹור:000000">de</a> <a name="01803603200008" ll="SDBH:אֹור:000000">relâmpagos</a>e os <a name="01803603200012" ll="SDBH:צוה:000000">dardeja</a> contra o <a name="01803603200018" ll="SDBH:פגע:000003">adversário</a>.
    
