\v 18 Ou <a name="01803701800002" ll="SDBH:רקע:000002">estendeste</a> com ele o <a name="01803701800008" ll="SDBH:שַׁחַק:000002">firmamento</a>,que é <a name="01803701800010" ll="SDBH:חָזָק:000001">sólido</a> como <a name="01803701800014" ll="SDBH:רְאִי:000000" il="Bolen00031">espelho</a> <a name="01803701800016" ll="SDBH:יצק:000004">fundido</a>?
    
\v 19 <a name="01803701900002">Ensina</a>-<a name="01803701900002">nos</a> o que lhe <a name="01803701900006" ll="SDBH:אמר:000000">diremos</a>;porque nós, <a name="01803701900016">envoltos</a> <a name="01803701900018" ll="SDBH:חֹשֶׁךְ:000000">em</a> <a name="01803701900018" ll="SDBH:חֹשֶׁךְ:000000">trevas</a>, nada lhe <a name="01803701900012" ll="SDBH:ערך:000000">podemos</a> <a name="01803701900012" ll="SDBH:ערך:000000">expor</a>.
    
\v 20 <a name="01803702000004" ll="SDBH:ספר:000006">Contar</a>-lhe-<a name="01803702000004" ll="SDBH:ספר:000006">ia</a> alguém o que <a name="01803702000010" ll="SDBH:דבר:001000" tl="HOTTP2040">tenho</a> <a name="01803702000010" ll="SDBH:דבר:001000" tl="HOTTP2040">dito</a>?Seria isso <a name="01803702000014" ll="SDBH:אמר:000000">desejar</a> o <a name="01803702000016">homem</a> <a name="01803702000020" ll="SDBH:בלע:000001;SDBH:בלע:000004">ser</a> <a name="01803702000020" ll="SDBH:בלע:000001;SDBH:בלע:000004">devorado</a>.
    
\v 21 Eis que o homem não pode <a name="01803702100008" ll="SDBH:ראה:000000">olhar</a> para o <a name="01803702100010" ll="SDBH:אֹור:000000">sol</a>,que <a name="01803702100012" ll="SDBH:בָּהִיר:000000;SDBH:בָּהִיר:001000">brilha</a> no <a name="01803702100020" ll="SDBH:שַׁחַק:000002">céu</a>,uma vez <a name="01803702100026">passado</a> o <a name="01803702100024" ll="SDBH:רוּחַ:000004" il="Gale_Force_Winds">vento</a> que <a name="01803702100030" ll="SDBH:טהר:000001">o</a> <a name="01803702100030" ll="SDBH:טהר:000001">deixa</a> <a name="01803702100030" ll="SDBH:טהר:000001">limpo</a>.
    
\v 22 Do <a name="01803702200004" ll="SDBH:צָפֹון:000001">norte</a> <a name="01803702200008" ll="SDBH:אתה:000002">vem</a> o <a name="01803702200006" ll="SDBH:זָהָב:000001">áureo</a> <a name="01803702200006" ll="SDBH:זָהָב:000001">esplendor</a>,pois <a name="01803702200012" ll="SDBH:אֱלֹוהַּ:000001" tl="HOTTP2041">Deus</a> está cercado de <a name="01803702200014" ll="SDBH:ירא:000001" tl="HOTTP2041">tremenda</a> <a name="01803702200016" ll="SDBH:הֹוד:000000" tl="HOTTP2041">majestade</a>.
    
\v 23 Ao <a name="01803702300002" ll="SDBH:שַׁדַּי:000000">Todo</a>-<a name="01803702300002" ll="SDBH:שַׁדַּי:000000">Poderoso</a>, não o <a name="01803702300006" ll="SDBH:מצא:000002">podemos</a> <a name="01803702300006" ll="SDBH:מצא:000002">alcançar</a>;ele é <a name="01803702300008" ll="SDBH:שַׂגִּיא:000002">grande</a> <a name="01803702300010" ll="SDBH:כֹּחַ:000000">em</a> <a name="01803702300010" ll="SDBH:כֹּחַ:000000">poder</a>,porém não <a name="01803702300024" ll="SDBH:ענה:001005">perverte</a> o <a name="01803702300014" ll="SDBH:מִשְׁפָּט:000007">juízo</a> e a <a name="01803702300018" ll="SDBH:רֹב:000001">plenitude</a> <a name="01803702300020" ll="SDBH:צְדָקָה:000001">da</a> <a name="01803702300020" ll="SDBH:צְדָקָה:000001">justiça</a>.
    
\v 24 Por isso, os homens <a name="01803702400004" ll="SDBH:ירא:000000">o</a> <a name="01803702400004" ll="SDBH:ירא:000000">temem</a>;ele não <a name="01803702400010" ll="SDBH:ראה:000000" tl="HOTTP2042">olha</a> para os que <a name="01803702400016" ll="SDBH:לֵב:000001">se</a> <a name="01803702400016" ll="SDBH:לֵב:000001">julgam</a> <a name="01803702400014" ll="SDBH:חָכָם:000000">sábios</a>.
