\v 1 Depois disto, <a name="01803800100006" ll="SDBH:יהוה:000000">o</a> <a name="01803800100006" ll="SDBH:יהוה:000000">Senhor</a>, do meio de um <a name="01803800100022" ll="SDBH:סְעָרָה:000000" il="Whirlwind">redemoinho</a>, <a name="01803800100004" ll="SDBH:ענה:000000">respondeu</a> a <a name="01803800100010" ll="SDBH:אִיֹּוב:000000">Jó</a>:
    
