\v 6 Sobre que <a name="01803800600008" ll="SDBH:טבע:000001">estão</a> <a name="01803800600008" ll="SDBH:טבע:000001">fundadas</a> as <a name="01803800600006" ll="SDBH:אֶדֶן:000000">suas</a> <a name="01803800600006" ll="SDBH:אֶדֶן:000000">bases</a>ou quem lhe <a name="01803800600014" ll="SDBH:ירה:000006">assentou</a> a <a name="01803800600016" ll="SDBH:אֶבֶן:000007" il="Realia:1.8.4c;il_quarry_transport_d01;jlm_quarrying_d01">pedra</a> <a name="01803800600018" ll="SDBH:פִּנָּה:000001">angular</a>,
    
\v 7 quando as <a name="01803800700008" ll="SDBH:כֹּוכָב:000000" il="Stars">estrelas</a> <a name="01803800700010" ll="SDBH:בֹּקֶר:000000">da</a> <a name="01803800700010" ll="SDBH:בֹּקֶר:000000">alva</a>, <a name="01803800700006">juntas</a>, alegremente <a name="01803800700004" ll="SDBH:רנן:000000">cantavam</a>,e <a name="01803800700014" ll="SDBH:רוע:000000">rejubilavam</a> todos os <a name="01803800700018" ll="SDBH:בֵּן:000003">filhos</a> de <a name="01803800700020" ll="SDBH:אֱלֹהִים:000001">Deus</a>?
    
