\v 10 Quando eu lhe <a name="01803801000004" ll="SDBH:שׁבר:000007">tracei</a> <a name="01803801000008" ll="SDBH:חֹק:000005">limites</a>,e lhe <a name="01803801000012" ll="SDBH:שׂים:000001">pus</a> <a name="01803801000014" ll="SDBH:בְּרִיחַ:000001">ferrolhos</a> e <a name="01803801000018" ll="SDBH:דֶּלֶת:000003">portas</a>,
    
