\v 12 Acaso, desde que começaram <a name="01803801200006">os</a> <a name="01803801200006">teus</a> <a name="01803801200006">dias</a>, <a name="01803801200008" ll="SDBH:יֹום:000004;SDBH:צוה:000000">deste</a> <a name="01803801200008" ll="SDBH:יֹום:000004;SDBH:צוה:000000">ordem</a> à <a name="01803801200010" ll="SDBH:צוה:000000">madrugada</a>ou <a name="01803801200016">fizeste</a> a <a name="01803801200022" ll="SDBH:שַׁחַר:000000" il="Sunrise;Sunset">alva</a> <a name="01803801200016">saber</a> o <a name="01803801200024" ll="SDBH:מָקֹום:000000">seu</a> <a name="01803801200024" ll="SDBH:מָקֹום:000000">lugar</a>,
    
