\v 18 <a name="01803801800002" ll="SDBH:בין:000002">Tens</a> <a name="01803801800002" ll="SDBH:בין:000002">ideia</a> <a name="01803801800002" ll="SDBH:בין:000002">nítida</a> da <a name="01803801800006" ll="SDBH:רַחַב:000000">largura</a> <a name="01803801800008" ll="SDBH:אֶרֶץ:000000" il="The_Earth">da</a> <a name="01803801800008" ll="SDBH:אֶרֶץ:000000" il="The_Earth">terra</a>?<a name="01803801800010" ll="SDBH:נגד:000000">Dize</a>-mo, se o <a name="01803801800014">sabes</a>.
    
