\v 15 Em toda aquela <a name="01804201500024" ll="SDBH:אֶרֶץ:000000">terra</a> não <a name="01804201500006" ll="SDBH:מצא:000017">se</a> <a name="01804201500006" ll="SDBH:מצא:000017">acharam</a> <a name="01804201500008" ll="SDBH:אִשָּׁה:000000">mulheres</a> tão <a name="01804201500010" ll="SDBH:יָפֶה:000000">formosas</a> como as <a name="01804201500014" ll="SDBH:בַּת:000000">filhas</a> de <a name="01804201500016" ll="SDBH:אִיֹּוב:000000">Jó</a>; e <a name="01804201500032" ll="SDBH:אָב:000000">seu</a> <a name="01804201500032" ll="SDBH:אָב:000000">pai</a> lhes <a name="01804201500028">deu</a> <a name="01804201500034" ll="SDBH:נַחֲלָה:000000">herança</a> <a name="01804201500038" ll="SDBH:תָּוֶךְ:000000">entre</a> <a name="01804201500040" ll="SDBH:אָח:000000">seus</a> <a name="01804201500040" ll="SDBH:אָח:000000">irmãos</a>. 
